<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>6760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>11080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，我在读一本关于动物的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11081</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我问了妈妈一个问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，动物都有尾巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为什么我们没有？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“动物需要尾巴，但是我们不需要。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我翻开了书的一页。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看这头海狮。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“海狮需要尾巴来游泳，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是我们可以用手和脚来游泳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有的动物用尾巴来赶走苍蝇。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，就像动物园里的斑马一样？”我问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说得对。但是我们用手来赶走苍蝇。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我又翻开书里的一页。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“袋鼠依靠尾巴坐起来。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有的动物的尾巴又大又强壮，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们用尾巴来捕食。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“像鳄鱼一样？”我问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错。你知道变色龙吗？”妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我知道！它可以改变自己身体的颜色。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说得对。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>变色龙的尾巴帮助它在树枝上保持平衡。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，动物们真的很需要尾巴！”我说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈接着说，“有的动物用尾巴来表演时尚秀。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我很好奇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么动物？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孔雀！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真有意思！”我说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想了想所有我知道的动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是妈妈，小猪不需要尾巴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！没错！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有的动物不像别的动物一样那么需要尾巴。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！玛菲在摇尾巴。”我说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈看了看玛菲大大的，毛茸茸的尾巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，她在打招呼，我们也向她打招呼吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛菲跳上了我的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我拍了拍她的头，她把尾巴摇得更欢了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165476</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“动物们真的需要尾巴呢！”我说。</Text>
